cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with medical image processing using a machine learning approach, specifically a convolutional neural network (CNN), for X-Ray image segmentation. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the challenges of working with small datasets, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of neural networks for image segmentation is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
